txt.en:
'The Orcs are trying to rally against us, raising the banners of Dol Guldur wherever they believe that they can bring forces together.

'Destroy those banners before they can gather to them. We must keep the forces in Gathbúrz scattered and leaderless while we attempt the gates of  Dol Guldur.

'When you have done as I have asked, return here to me.'
'Well struck, [placeholder]. The Orcs may rally to ashes and fear for today. Thanks to you, their banners stand no more!'
'We will not tolerate the presence of our enemies in this, our home of old! Burn their banners, [placeholder]!'
The Orcs of Gathbúrz are rasing banners of Dol Guldur in an attempt to rally against the Malledhrim onslaught.
Banners of Dol Guldur can be found throughout Gathbúrz.
Rodelleth is at Thangúlhad in Gathbúrz.\n\nYou should return to Rodelleth with tidings of your success.
